node.text:
On this special date, we celebrate all of our ladies around the world killing in the engineering field. Power to you all!!! We had the amazing opportunity to talk to @stemathome_ @hellonikkib @luisapanucio @bmekween and @papayatutor CEO and Founder @sv0888 taking over my account to shed light on their journey while reviewing some memes. 

I am proud to be a #maleally and respect all of your for staying in a challenging career - not just because it is brain stimulating, but because of all the biases and stereotypes that exist in this field. You are all my hero! 

@papayatutor started this initiative because they aim to serve nontraditional STEM students. As of now, women are considered one. However, @sv0888 has joined forces with me and @stemedia to change the narrative for women all over the world 

You can watch this on @stemedia youtube channel or read the blog on @papayatutor. 

If you need a tutor, use my code FREE30 to get a special discount. 

This is brought to you by @papayatutor in partnership @lumisautomation to help you engineer the world of tomorrow 

@stemedia to elevate and empower your STEM journey 

#womeninstem #femaleempoweremet #womeninengineering #stem #engineerstudent

node.text:
Special thanks to the @battlebots team and Greg for inviting me to their World Championships in Las Vegas. I appreciate the hospitality and making me feel like a celebrity 😎. I remember watching the show years back and thinking how cool it is. One day I saw they were following me and decided to send them a DM for a collaboration, it’s amazing how sending a message can open such doors. Catch them on @discovery channel.Till next time!

#battlebots #worldchampionships #behindthescenes #itsrobotfightingtime
